delete the pattern from the argument list instead
of reporting an error.  Overrides @t{NOMATCH}.

@pindex NUMERIC_GLOB_SORT
@pindex NO_NUMERIC_GLOB_SORT
@pindex NUMERICGLOBSORT
@pindex NONUMERICGLOBSORT
