@subsection Modifying Text
@noindent
@table @asis
@tindex vi-add-eol
@item @t{vi-add-eol} (unbound) (@t{A}) (unbound)
Move to the end of the line and enter insert mode.

@tindex vi-add-next
@item @t{vi-add-next} (unbound) (@t{a}) (unbound)
