@tindex backward-delete-char
@item @t{backward-delete-char} (@t{^H ^?}) (unbound) (unbound)
Delete the character behind the cursor.

@tindex vi-backward-delete-char
@item @t{vi-backward-delete-char} (unbound) (@t{X}) (@t{^H})
