@tindex quote-region
@item @t{quote-region} (@t{ESC-"}) (unbound) (unbound)
Quote the region from the cursor to the mark.

@tindex vi-replace
@item @t{vi-replace} (unbound) (@t{R}) (unbound)
Enter overwrite mode.

