@item @t{fned} [ @t{-x} @var{num} ] @var{name}
Same as @t{zed -f}.  This function does not appear in the zsh
distribution, but can be created by linking @t{zed} to the name @t{fned}
in some directory in your @t{fpath}.

@findex histed
